Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.25,0:00:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme music plays]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.54,0:01:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,GLARE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.17,0:01:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That was footage from surveillance cameras\Nat the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.46,0:01:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The death of one of the FBI agents\Nis captured on here. [groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.84,0:01:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see the following scenes again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.60,0:01:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Raye Penber passing the ticket gate\Non his way in,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.10,0:01:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,then him boarding the train. And finally,\Nthe part where he dies on the platform.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.23,0:01:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[Shuichi Aizawa] Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.60,0:01:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.77,0:01:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's next to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.02,0:01:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.52,0:01:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, so based on the records I have here,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.03,0:01:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Raye Penber comes through\Nthe west entrance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.90,0:01:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,of Shinjuku Station at 3:11 p.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.16,0:02:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Then at 3:13 he boards a train\Non the Yamanote Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.41,0:02:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But even if he was following someone\Nat that time,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.75,0:02:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's going to be very difficult\Nfor us to draw any real conclusions
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.04,0:02:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,from this blurry video.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.63,0:02:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And then at exactly 4:42 p.m. ...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.05,0:02:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you very much, Watari.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.26,0:02:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, and at 4:42 p.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.88,0:02:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,he exits the train at Tokyo station\Nand dies on the platform.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.80,0:02:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quite strange, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.43,0:02:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, what do you find strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.60,0:02:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, what is it?\NDid you notice something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.02,0:02:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm...\NWe know that Raye Penber got on the train
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.69,0:02:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and then an hour and a half later\Nhe got off and died on the platform.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.90,0:02:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Yamanote Line only takes an hour\Nto complete its circuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.36,0:02:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And more importantly,\Nthere's the envelope.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.32,0:02:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,-What do you mean?\N-[remote beeps]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.12,0:02:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] He's holding\Nwhat looks like an envelope
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.08,0:02:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,when he passes through the ticket gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps] You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.25,0:02:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's there, under his arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.29,0:02:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But in the footage right before his death\Nit's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.76,0:02:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you actually caught that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.76,0:03:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't see an envelope\Non this list of his personal effects.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.43,0:03:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Which means it was left in the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.43,0:03:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you watch closely\Nat the very end here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.39,0:03:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,it seems like he's straining\Nto look inside the train
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.94,0:03:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,before the doors close.\NYou can see right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.40,0:03:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case,\Ndo you think it could mean something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.90,0:03:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be interesting\Nif Kira was on that train?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.57,0:03:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.28,0:03:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I admit I find it hard to believe as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.24,0:03:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no reason for Kira\Nto come to the scene of his own crime
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.83,0:03:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,when he can kill from a distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.33,0:03:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... maybe he was counting on us\Nto make that assumption,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.08,0:03:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and figured he could get away with\Nsuch a bold move.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.30,0:03:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] What's going on with you, Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.51,0:03:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't stopped writing\Ncriminals' names in the Death Note
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.39,0:03:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,for four days straight.\NSo what are you trying to prove?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.10,0:03:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see the point in writing\Nthese names weeks in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.27,0:03:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen the Death Note\Nused like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.44,0:03:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Consider it insurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.98,0:04:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Suppose the son of\Nthe Detective Superintendent of the NPA
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.28,0:04:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,was hospitalized,\Nif criminals stop dying at the same time
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.20,0:04:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,it wouldn't be difficult\Nto connect the two.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.45,0:04:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.04,0:04:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure that I can use any date
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.95,0:04:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,as long as it's before the end\Nof a person's predetermined lifespan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.33,0:04:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I can't guarantee it, because\Nwe Shinigami don't normally work that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.92,0:04:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But I suppose any time before the end\Nof their lifespan should work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.34,0:04:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I really can't count on you, can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.22,0:04:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You got that right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.18,0:04:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[Watari] Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.76,0:04:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, would you please hold\Nfor a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.81,0:04:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.35,0:04:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Ukita at the NPA.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.35,0:04:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He says he's on the phone with someone
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.06,0:04:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,from the tip-line\Nwho has information for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.36,0:04:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Then give Ukita the number\Nfor line five
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.07,0:04:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and ask him to have the informant\Ncall that line instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.86,0:04:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be safer that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.41,0:04:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Matsuda, it's okay for you\Nto turn on your cell phone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, please turn it on right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.41,0:04:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.08,0:04:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[phone rings]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.87,0:04:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-[phone beeps]\N-Yes, this is Suzuki,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.79,0:05:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,head of Kira's investigation\NPublic Information division.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.67,0:05:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Raye Penber's fiancée?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.88,0:05:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Naomi Misora...\NI've heard that name before...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.18,0:05:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.64,0:05:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] So it's her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.85,0:05:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She from the Los Angeles BB murder case.\NThat's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.60,0:05:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,She was working under me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.61,0:05:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess she must have come to Japan\Nwith her fiancée.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.53,0:05:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[phone beeps]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.95,0:05:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well apparently she's been missing\Nsince the day after her fiancé died.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.28,0:05:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that anyone in her situation\Nwould be pretty depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.54,0:05:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it… suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.67,0:05:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the Naomi Misora I knew\Nwas strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.58,0:05:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention that she was also\Nan excellent FBI agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.80,0:05:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything, it's more likely\Nthat she'd be trying to catch Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.01,0:05:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears she came to Japan\Nwith Penber.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.64,0:05:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's possible she may have found a lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.68,0:05:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] If that's the case,\Ndid Kira manage to get to her first?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.52,0:06:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, from this point,\NI'd like to focus our investigation
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.15,0:06:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,on only those people\Nwhom Raye Penber was tailing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.19,0:06:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,In particular,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.28,0:06:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,he was assigned to two police officers\Nand those closest to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.74,0:06:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well, who are these two individuals\Nhe was investigating?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.24,0:06:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Deputy Director General Kitamura,\Nalong with…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.00,0:06:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Detective Superintendent Yagami,\Nand their families.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.92,0:06:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,At this stage, I'd like to place wiretaps\Nand surveillance cameras
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.88,0:06:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,in both households.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.55,0:06:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light Yagami] I have to make there's\Nno evidence left on this computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.43,0:06:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,just in case someone goes through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.76,0:06:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I just have to hide these clippings\Nfrom the Death Note in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.64,0:06:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] It seems like you're pretty skilled\Nwith your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.69,0:06:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you're pretty popular\Nwith the girls, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.44,0:06:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Skill has nothing to do with it.\NIt's your looks that count.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.32,0:06:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm guessing you're not that popular,\Nare you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.16,0:06:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.49,0:06:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[Touta Matsuda]\NSurveillance cameras? Ryuzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.78,0:06:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] I don't see how\Nyou could even consider this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.04,0:06:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If this got out, we'd have\Na civil rights scandal on our hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.62,0:07:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd all lose our jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.92,0:07:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You told me you'd be willing\Nto risk your lives for this investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.84,0:07:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But you wouldn't risk your jobs?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.76,0:07:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuzaki, what are the odds that Kira is\Nin one of those households?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.34,0:07:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe ten percent.\NNo, it's closer to five percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.64,0:07:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.77,0:07:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,-Sorry, but it's not worth the risk.\N-[Yagami] No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.89,0:07:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Of all the people\Nwe've investigated so far,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.35,0:07:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,not one of them seemed\Neven the least bit suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.52,0:07:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if there's only a one percent chance,\Nwe simply can't afford to ignore it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.28,0:07:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.44,0:07:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to tell you how offended I am\Nto learn my family is under suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.87,0:07:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-Having said that, just go ahead with it.\N-[both gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.99,0:07:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] And make sure\Nyou install them everywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.00,0:07:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want any blind spots in the house,\Nand that includes the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.96,0:07:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.\NThat was my intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.75,0:07:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Chief.\NYou don't have to agree to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.13,0:07:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he's right.\NThink about your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.17,0:07:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a wife\Nand daughter at home, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.26,0:07:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm well aware of that fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.39,0:07:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's no point in doing any of this\Nif we can't be thorough!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.35,0:07:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I suggest you keep quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.43,0:08:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[both gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.89,0:08:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Matsuda] I'm sorry.\N-No, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.02,0:08:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.36,0:08:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,As a courtesy to the Chief and his family,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.99,0:08:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,only he and I will conduct surveillance\Nof their home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.57,0:08:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Watari, how long will it take to prepare\Nthe wiretaps and cameras we need?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.33,0:08:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, starting tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.04,0:08:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I can set them up at any time
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.92,0:08:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,provided we know when\Nboth houses will be empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.55,0:08:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[man] See you later, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.09,0:08:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.22,0:08:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What? No one's home yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.94,0:08:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.16,0:08:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,-[handle clicks]\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.04,0:09:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.33,0:09:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] How's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.37,0:09:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think anyone else is in\Nthe house right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.92,0:09:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you wanna play some video games?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.30,0:09:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, it's been awhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.59,0:09:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.26,0:09:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.85,0:09:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] I don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.61,0:09:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I never knew he went\Nto such great lengths.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What could he be hiding in there\Nthat he doesn't want anyone else to see?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.45,0:09:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,For a 17-year-old kid,\NI wouldn't say this kind of behavior
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.41,0:09:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,is particularly abnormal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.49,0:09:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was his age,\NI did strange things too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.33,0:09:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever talked to you son\Nabout the investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.66,0:09:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.71,0:09:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never once revealed\Nclassified information to my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.29,0:09:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I don't get to see them\Ntoo often these days,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.38,0:09:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and usually as soon as I get home\Nall I can do is sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.51,0:09:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.97,0:10:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Where exactly are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.14,0:10:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Light, don’t ignore me\Nwhen I'm talking to you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.56,0:10:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,or I'll get mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.65,0:10:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Light] Doesn't look ...\N-[Ryuk] Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.11,0:10:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,...like these clothes have been bugged.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.94,0:10:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yoo-hoo!\N-[Light] I think we're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.82,0:10:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.78,0:10:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a very strong possibility\Nthat there are wiretaps,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.49,0:10:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and maybe even surveillance cameras,\Nhidden throughout my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.91,0:10:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? But that piece of paper\Nwas still in your door, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.99,0:10:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-That's true, but...\N-I left the paper in the door in a way
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.91,0:10:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that it would be obvious\Nto anyone entering the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.21,0:10:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,-The real test is the handle.\N-It is?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.17,0:10:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,When that door is closed,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.30,0:10:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the door handle automatically returns\Nto a horizontal position
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.92,0:10:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and it won't go any higher than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.01,0:10:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But whenever I close the door,\NI adjust it slightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.72,0:10:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of letting it sit horizontally,\NI lower it by about five millimeters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.89,0:10:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,When I get home and try to open the door,\Nif the handle is all the way up,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I can be fairly certain\Nthat someone was in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.65,0:10:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But that method alone doesn't tell me\Nif my door was actually opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.28,0:10:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So I also put a mechanical\Npencil lead in place as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.36,0:11:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So what do you do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.99,0:11:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It goes on the hinge.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.70,0:11:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,After I close the door,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.87,0:11:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I take the pencil lead\Nand rest it on the hinges
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.12,0:11:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,in such a way that it will break if\Nthe door happens to be opened by anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.37,0:11:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally I take it out myself\Nwhen I get back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.54,0:11:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,When I got home from school today,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.09,0:11:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I noticed that the pencil lead was broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.38,0:11:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it,\NI do remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.05,0:11:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,First the door handle,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.59,0:11:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,then the lead.\NI know someone was in there today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.26,0:11:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it was your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.10,0:11:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,My family wouldn't have noticed\Nthe piece of paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.68,0:11:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What's suspicious is that someone\Ntook the time to put it back in the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.27,0:11:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,PSYCHOLOGY\NPSYCHOTHERAPY
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.35,0:11:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[woman] Hi there, can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.86,0:11:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this all about?\NAre you buying a book
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.98,0:11:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,about wiretaps and surveillance\Nso you can figure this mess out?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.78,0:11:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,SHOGEN BOOKS
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.95,0:11:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Ryuk,\Nwhat about your apples?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.24,0:11:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Apples?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.74,0:11:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! That's right, surveillance cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.16,0:11:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Once the apple's in my mouth,\Nno one can see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.00,0:11:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But while I'm holding it,\Nit looks like it's floating.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.54,0:11:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.92,0:11:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You told me that Shinigami can't die,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.42,0:12:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,so I guess it won't kill you\Nto stop eating apples for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.30,0:12:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[grumbles] Don't you think\Nthat's a bit much? Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.97,0:12:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I never told you this,\Nbut apples are to me
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.60,0:12:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,what cigarettes and alcohol are to humans.\NDo you see what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.43,0:12:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I even get withdrawal symptoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.94,0:12:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Oh yeah?\NWhat kind of symptoms?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.19,0:12:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,My body gets all twisted.\NI do handstands. It's not pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.61,0:12:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,-I don't want to see that.\N-I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.19,0:12:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, here's the thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.03,0:12:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, I already gave L the hint\Nthat Shinigami love apples,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.28,0:12:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,so I just can't afford\Nto take the risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.16,0:12:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.12,0:12:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's so important for you\Nto eat apples...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.29,0:12:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll have to find out\Nwhere all the cameras are hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.25,0:12:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're lucky,\Nyou might find a blind spot
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.25,0:12:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,where you can eat them\Nwithout being seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.88,0:12:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.68,0:12:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! the camera search.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.72,0:12:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] Sounds so interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.29,0:13:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh... I have to find the cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.38,0:13:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe my son is looking at\Nthose magazines.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.38,0:13:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's normal for a 17-year-old.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.09,0:13:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But it seems contrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.26,0:13:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.51,0:13:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The only reason he didn't want anyone\Nin his room
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.98,0:13:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,was because he had these magazines?\NThat's what he wants us to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.77,0:13:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's my son\Nyou're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.02,0:13:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you honestly telling me\Nthat you suspect him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.69,0:13:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I do suspect him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.48,0:13:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I placed wiretaps\Nand surveillance cameras in your house
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.28,0:13:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and the Deputy Director's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.70,0:13:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.07,0:13:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I found a camera in the air conditioner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.20,0:13:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.75,0:13:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So, they really put cameras\Nin here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.79,0:13:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They must have bugged the place\Nas well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.25,0:13:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if this is the Kira case,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.75,0:14:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think the Japanese police\Nwould ever go this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.92,0:14:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be L's idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.38,0:14:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means they've narrowed down\Ntheir list of suspects.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.26,0:14:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,By now they must have figured out\Nthat it was someone
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.30,0:14:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,who Raye Penber was investigating,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.55,0:14:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,or they wouldn't have gone to\Nall this trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.43,0:14:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.52,0:14:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, these covers mislead you\Nall the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.98,0:14:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.11,0:14:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Given the situation, it's safer if\NI just assume I'm their prime suspect,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.98,0:14:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and the only one being watched.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.03,0:14:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.65,0:14:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Luckily I prepared for\Nthis kind of situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.41,0:14:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Light…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.62,0:14:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Light!\NCome on, dinner's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[man on TV] I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.59,0:14:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Always.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.34,0:14:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.26,0:14:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hideki Ryuga.\NI swear he's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.39,0:14:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How come no one in my class\Nis like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.14,0:15:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayu, just eat your dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.90,0:15:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[Sayu Yagami] I'll eat later!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.36,0:15:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Mr. Aizawa? Are the Kitamuras\Nwatching television now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.86,0:15:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.07,0:15:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not home, but the other four\Nare watching while they eat dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.41,0:15:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's channel four.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.87,0:15:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Watari, please contact the broadcasters\Nand tell them to play our message.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.83,0:15:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[Watari] Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.58,0:15:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,NKK NEWS FLASH
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.75,0:15:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[Sayu] Huh? What this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.58,0:15:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The ICPO?\NThey're saying that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.71,0:15:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,"In response to the Kira murders,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.71,0:15:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Interpol has decided to dispatch a force\Nof 1500 investigators to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.47,0:15:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The investigators were drawn from\Nthe law enforcement agencies
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.18,0:15:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,of its member nations.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.01,0:15:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Fifteen hundred investigators
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.35,0:15:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Woah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.31,0:15:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Chances are they've got cameras\Nin the living room as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.15,0:15:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Regardless of whether\Nthis news is real or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.69,0:15:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,it's obvious they're just trying to evoke\Na reaction from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.98,0:15:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,L, it's the exact same trick\Nyou used last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.53,0:15:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-The ICPO sure is stupid.\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.70,0:15:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, there's no point\Nin making this announcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.37,0:16:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If they're going to send\Nall these people here to investigate
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.87,0:16:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,shouldn't they keep it a secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.04,0:16:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the FBI agents who were secretly\Ninvestigating were killed by Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.00,0:16:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would this be any different?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.71,0:16:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If you ask me, this is nothing more than\Na desperate attempt
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.34,0:16:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,to shock Kira, in the hopes that\Nhe'll reveal himself somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.18,0:16:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite frankly, I wouldn't be surprise\Nif Kira sees right through this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.06,0:16:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles quietly]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.02,0:16:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Your son is clever, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.31,0:16:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. Well, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.44,0:16:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Thanks for dinner, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.52,0:16:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[Sayu] Huh?\NYou're eating a bag of chips?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.77,0:16:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You just had dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.78,0:16:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Your looks will go\Nif you keep that up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.40,0:16:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a late-night snack for studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.95,0:16:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's it, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.74,0:16:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I found every camera\Nthey put in the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.37,0:16:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess even Shinigami get tired\Nwhen they work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.63,0:16:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let me explain where they all are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.13,0:16:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a little bit complicated,\Nso listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.84,0:16:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing I hate more\Nthan explaining something twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.05,0:16:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] All right, time for me\Nto hit the books.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.05,0:16:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] There sure are\Na lot of cameras in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.60,0:17:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I counted 64 in total.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.02,0:17:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess whoever put them here\Nexpected you'd at least find some of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.02,0:17:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] It has to be L.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.61,0:17:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He had no qualms about putting\Na death row inmate in his place
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.78,0:17:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,when he declared war on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.69,0:17:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty clear he doesn't know\Nany limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.07,0:17:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh. What I want to know is,\Nhow am I going to be able to eat apples?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.99,0:17:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Obviously that's impossible now,\Nisn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.41,0:17:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, I guess you can't talk in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.54,0:17:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But we better discuss this\Noutside tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.54,0:17:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I think I'm getting\Nthe hang of this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.96,0:17:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Judging from the number of cameras\Nhe's planted,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.26,0:17:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,he's planning to make a decision\Nwithin a short period of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.63,0:17:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Any normal person would slip\Nunder these circumstances,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.64,0:17:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,but it won't be that easy with me, L.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.31,0:17:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the closest you will get!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.40,0:17:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.61,0:18:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] I've set things up so that\Ncriminals will continue to die
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.33,0:18:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,over the next three weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.95,0:18:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,L is aware by now that Kira can control\Nthe times of death of his victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.37,0:18:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, to avoid suspicion,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.17,0:18:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,L needs to see criminals\Nwhose names are being broadcast
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.88,0:18:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,continue to die while I have no access\Nto that information.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.72,0:18:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.01,0:18:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The symptoms are starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.43,0:18:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] I'm going to show you, L!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.56,0:18:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,With Ryuk's information\Nand my preparations,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.65,0:18:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I can continue to kill criminals\Nwhose names are broadcast on the news,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.52,0:18:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,while masquerading as\Nas a typical high school student
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.36,0:18:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,studying for his entrance exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.20,0:18:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Just watch me, L.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.78,0:18:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll solve equations with my right hand\Nand write names with my left.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.04,0:18:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,MURAO TA....
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.95,0:18:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,SUSPECT: TAYOSHI MURAO
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.91,0:18:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] I'll take a potato chip...\Nand eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.80,0:19:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] After dinner,\Nyour son just goes back to studying
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.22,0:19:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,without turning on\Nthe TV or his computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.77,0:19:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because the entrance exams\Nare five days away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.45,0:19:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Now, a criminal\Nwho I should have no knowledge of
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.03,0:19:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,will die of a heart attack\Nin forty seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.24,0:19:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And the witness to my alibi is L himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.71,0:19:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, just a little bit longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.47,0:19:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.84,0:19:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Watari?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.76,0:19:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,A few minutes ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.97,0:19:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,a bank clerk being questioned\Non suspicion of embezzlement,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.56,0:19:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and a purse-snatcher\Nbeing held in a detention center
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.60,0:19:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,were broadcast on the news...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.27,0:19:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They both just died of sudden,\Ninexplicable heart attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.32,0:19:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's him again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.15,0:20:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,While all that was happening at your home,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.28,0:20:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,your wife and daughter\Nwere watching television.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.32,0:20:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,When that was over, they turned the TV off\Nand didn't watch anything afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.79,0:20:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,From just past seven thirty\Nuntil now, eleven o'clock,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.71,0:20:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,your son's done nothing but study.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.83,0:20:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira needs a name and a face.\NWithout those, he can't kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.80,0:20:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So I suppose anyone who didn't watch\Nthe news can't be Kira, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.09,0:20:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You said it yourself, that means\Nmy family has been cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.39,0:20:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't make sense\Nthat Kira would kill two petty criminals
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.68,0:20:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,right after\Ntheir identities were broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.06,0:20:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.48,0:20:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's only the first day\Nafter the cameras were installed,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.44,0:20:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,but the Yagami household seems\Nalmost too innocent to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.69,0:20:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.95,0:20:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light's mom]\NLight, are you up yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.82,0:20:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Yeah, I'm awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.95,0:20:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is garbage day, so if you've got\Nany, bring it down with you, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.04,0:20:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] What a pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.54,0:20:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light's mom]\NWhat are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.67,0:20:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You usually say,\N"There's no need to remind me, Mom."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.34,0:21:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Yeah, yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.30,0:21:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.47,0:21:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Another beautiful day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.01,0:21:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I can't say for sure\Nwhether you're extremely generous
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.77,0:21:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,or just a spoiled brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.85,0:21:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But didn't that mini-LCD TV cost you\N400 bucks?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.94,0:21:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light's mom] Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.45,0:21:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,TO BE CONTINUED
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.88,0:21:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme music plays]